{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"童话说","keywords":["tonghuashuo","github","front-end","javascript","typescript","react","node","washington","hua","童话","童话说","前端","博客","技术","计算机","互联网"]}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>用CSS3绘图并不是什么新鲜事，业内有很多大牛都已经尝试过。借着中秋，我们就来画个月饼试试吧。</p>\n<p>PS：考虑到我并非学美术出身，美观度方面还请各位多多包涵。</p>\n<p>PPS：建议使用Chrome浏览器（或其它webkit、blink内核的浏览器）查看，效果最佳。</p>\n<h2>基本结构</h2>\n<p>我把月饼大致分为四个部分：主体圆形、周围的花边、面上的纹理、中间的字。</p>\n<h2>主体圆形</h2>\n<p>利用 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">border-radius</code> 来绘制圆形，这是CSS3绘图中最基本的一个方法。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.main</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #C76603<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px solid #BA3B00<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>main<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>我将背景设为 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">position: relative;</code> ，以便其中的元素能够进行绝对定位。使用CSS3绘图时，我们会用到大量的绝对定位。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d4a0277d2f4bb65e786f65bc9b535278/5992f/01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 86.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d4a0277d2f4bb65e786f65bc9b535278/5992f/01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d4a0277d2f4bb65e786f65bc9b535278/9995a/01.jpg 240w,\n/static/d4a0277d2f4bb65e786f65bc9b535278/b7826/01.jpg 480w,\n/static/d4a0277d2f4bb65e786f65bc9b535278/5992f/01.jpg 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2>周围的花边</h2>\n<p>花边的本质也是圆，只不过小一点。这里为了计算方便，我画了12个，当然真正的月饼肯定不止这么多，只是我偷懒了，因为纯CSS3的环境下没法进行表达式计算，如果借助JavaScript或是LESS、SCSS、SASS的力量，我们就可以很方便地控制数量，想画多少个就画多少个。</p>\n<p>每个小圆通过绝对定位进行放置，结合圆心的坐标以及三角函数关系，就能确定每个小圆的坐标位置。注意，由于盒模型的关系，计算出小圆的圆心坐标之后，还要减去半径，得到盒子左上角的坐标才对。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1b62be50b384faee54eca367bc638663/5992f/02-01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 86.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-02-01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1b62be50b384faee54eca367bc638663/5992f/02-01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1b62be50b384faee54eca367bc638663/9995a/02-01.jpg 240w,\n/static/1b62be50b384faee54eca367bc638663/b7826/02-01.jpg 480w,\n/static/1b62be50b384faee54eca367bc638663/5992f/02-01.jpg 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>每个小圆之间是互相叠加的，细心的朋友应该会发现了，最后一个圆会覆盖到第一个圆上，使其变成最下面一层，破坏了连贯性。这里我们用一点点小技巧来解决。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/67804eec8f60cbfb3cb2bcdadfdedfbe/3833b/02-02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-02-02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/67804eec8f60cbfb3cb2bcdadfdedfbe/3833b/02-02.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/67804eec8f60cbfb3cb2bcdadfdedfbe/bf594/02-02.jpg 240w,\n/static/67804eec8f60cbfb3cb2bcdadfdedfbe/3833b/02-02.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>首先我们要让0点方向的圆的左半边重新回到最上层，因此我们把0点位置的圆复制一下，再利用 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">border-radius</code> 将其变成一个半圆，这样一来，左边就重新出现了。（为了便于理解，这里我改变了一下半圆的颜色和层叠关系）</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.ear.index12</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px 0 0 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>ear index12<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8a8c087d2edec8a958d350b6ba2887e9/3833b/02-03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-02-03\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8a8c087d2edec8a958d350b6ba2887e9/3833b/02-03.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a8c087d2edec8a958d350b6ba2887e9/bf594/02-03.jpg 240w,\n/static/8a8c087d2edec8a958d350b6ba2887e9/3833b/02-03.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a>\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/556d3561218ebeb9d6910703d81ebfd4/3833b/02-04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-02-04\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/556d3561218ebeb9d6910703d81ebfd4/3833b/02-04.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/556d3561218ebeb9d6910703d81ebfd4/bf594/02-04.jpg 240w,\n/static/556d3561218ebeb9d6910703d81ebfd4/3833b/02-04.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>但这也带来了一个新问题：半圆右边有一条竖线。解决办法有两个，一个是单独设置半圆的 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">border-right-color: transparent;</code> ，这个方法有效但并不完美，仔细观察会发现顶部留有一个小小的缺口。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f08569c6ffe7119b97e235afd4635526/1caba/02-05.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 400px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-02-05\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f08569c6ffe7119b97e235afd4635526/1caba/02-05.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f08569c6ffe7119b97e235afd4635526/38c71/02-05.jpg 240w,\n/static/f08569c6ffe7119b97e235afd4635526/1caba/02-05.jpg 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>另一个方案就是用一个略小一点的色块来把这条线盖住，这里我们采用的就是这种方法，将半圆复制一下，并进行一定的调整，使其刚好能把这条竖线藏起来，同时又不会挡到1点中方向的小圆。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.ear.index13</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 42px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 25px 0 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #C76603<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>ear index13<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c331f3ec3ef8210b60beb66cd95a9656/3833b/02-06.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-02-06\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c331f3ec3ef8210b60beb66cd95a9656/3833b/02-06.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c331f3ec3ef8210b60beb66cd95a9656/bf594/02-06.jpg 240w,\n/static/c331f3ec3ef8210b60beb66cd95a9656/3833b/02-06.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2>面上的纹理</h2>\n<p>表面的纹理我选择了十字交错的直线，主要是因为圆形已经用得够多了，想换个风格。我们先从一个直角开始，剩下的只要旋转并对齐就好了。</p>\n<p>这里我选择了 <code class=\"gatsby-code-ul\">li</code> 的结构来实现，因为本质上这就是一个由不同长度的线段组成的等距线段列表。只要把 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">ul</code> 定好位，然后通过不断的尝试，设定最佳的数量和长度即可。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">ul</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">ul.top-qu</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 128px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 227px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-90deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px solid #BA3B00<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 11px 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">list-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li:first-child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li:nth-child(2)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 55px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 80px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li:nth-child(3)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 85px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 60px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>top-qu<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> // 重复10个\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4116739f87e769439dbbd2e0b3ee51e3/5992f/03-01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 83.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-03-01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4116739f87e769439dbbd2e0b3ee51e3/5992f/03-01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4116739f87e769439dbbd2e0b3ee51e3/9995a/03-01.jpg 240w,\n/static/4116739f87e769439dbbd2e0b3ee51e3/b7826/03-01.jpg 480w,\n/static/4116739f87e769439dbbd2e0b3ee51e3/5992f/03-01.jpg 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p> <code class=\"gatsby-code-ul\">li</code> 默认是竖着往下的，也就是朝向3点钟方向的那一个直角。因此其它3个方向的部分需要借助 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">transform: rotate(90deg);</code> 来实现旋转，再调整 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">top</code> 和 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">left</code> 来进行对齐，就完成了。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/472c3d85a91f875f3a966731efb8114e/5992f/03-02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 83.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-03-02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/472c3d85a91f875f3a966731efb8114e/5992f/03-02.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/472c3d85a91f875f3a966731efb8114e/9995a/03-02.jpg 240w,\n/static/472c3d85a91f875f3a966731efb8114e/b7826/03-02.jpg 480w,\n/static/472c3d85a91f875f3a966731efb8114e/5992f/03-02.jpg 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2>中间的字</h2>\n<p>字的部分就很简单了，在 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">div.text</code> 里用两个 <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">p</code> 写好文字，设置好间距，定好位，给点圆角，就OK了。注意，这里需要给文字的边框设置一下背景色，否则它就是透明的，底下的十字交错结构会显示出来。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 160px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 160px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #C76603<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px solid #BA3B00<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.text p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 80px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 80px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #BA3B00<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"gatsby-code-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>快中<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>乐秋<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d9cb9dbdfe64102de172d1e9cdfb5944/5992f/04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 83.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css3-mooncake-04\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d9cb9dbdfe64102de172d1e9cdfb5944/5992f/04.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d9cb9dbdfe64102de172d1e9cdfb5944/9995a/04.jpg 240w,\n/static/d9cb9dbdfe64102de172d1e9cdfb5944/b7826/04.jpg 480w,\n/static/d9cb9dbdfe64102de172d1e9cdfb5944/5992f/04.jpg 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2>小结</h2>\n<p>使用 CSS3 进行图形的绘制，从减轻网络传输负载、提高浏览器渲染效率的角度上讲，是非常好的一个技巧。从技术上讲，只要能把原图产分成基本几何形状的，都能用 CSS3 来实现。但这项技术最大的不足在于代码编写较为费时费力，涉及大量的定位和数值计算工作，重复性劳动较多，因此实战中只能用于元素较为简单的情况，过于复杂的绘图要求在进度上会比较吃力。</p>\n<p>业余时间用 CSS3 画点小东西，主要是为了熟悉 CSS3 的一些使用技巧，像盒模型的边框、定位、旋转、斜切，以及如何利用这些基础的东西搭建起一个相对复杂一些的玩意儿。就像是乐高玩具，本身很简单，但发挥想象力，我们可以用它塑造出很多有意思的东西。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"纯 CSS3 绘制月饼","description":"中秋佳节，用CSS3来画个月饼吧","date":"2015-09-27","cover":{"publicURL":"/static/css3-mooncake-9aaefaae86216c79623893c080f1ccc2.jpg"},"tags":["css","mooncake","project"],"series":null,"draft":null},"fields":{"id":"css3-mooncake","date":"2015-09-26T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2015/09/27/css3-mooncake"}}